# Bug File Template

```markdown
# {ID} — {Title}

## Description
[What's happening vs what should happen]

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Step 1
2. Step 2

## Expected Behavior
[What should happen]

## Actual Behavior
[What happens instead]

## Root Cause
[Fill after investigation]

## Fix
[Fill after resolution — what was changed and why]

## Status
- **Severity**: ASAP / Critical / High / Medium / Low
- **Status**: Open / In progress / In review / Blocked / Resolved / Cannot reproduce / Duplicate / Won't fix
- **Created**: YYYY-MM-DD
- **Resolved**: YYYY-MM-DD (fill when done)
- **Commit**: [hash] (fill when done)
- **Blocked reason**: (fill if Blocked)
- **Duplicate of**: (fill if Duplicate — link to original)
```
